'''阿薩姆聯合解放陣線'''（United Liberation Front of Asom）是在[[印度东北地区|印度东北地区]]多个分离组织中之一，成立于1979年，並在1990年正式活動<ref name="satp"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2016-01-24/news/70036465_1_anup-chetia-bangladesh-jail-assam-assembly|title=Why the militant group ULFA matters ahead of Assam Assembly Polls|access-date=2019-12-28}}</ref>。该组织谋求通过[[武装斗争|武装斗争]]来建立自治政府<ref name="satp">{{cite web|url=http://www.satp.org/satporgtp/countries/india/states/assam/terrorist_outfits/Ulfa.htm |title=United Liberation Front of Asom (ULFA) - Terrorist Group of Assam |publisher=Satp.org |access-date=2013-01-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://yaleglobal.yale.edu/content/indias-treacherous-northeast|title=India's Treacherous Northeast|date=2012-09-26|publisher=Yaleglobal.yale.edu|access-date=2014-10-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://mha.gov.in/node/91173|title=Banned Organizations {{!}} Ministry of Home Affairs {{!}} GoI|website=mha.gov.in|access-date=2019-12-28}}</ref>。於1990年被[[印度政府|印度政府]]定性為[[恐怖組織|恐怖組織]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nia.gov.in/banned_org.aspx|title=NIA :: Banned Terrorist Organisations|publisher=Nia.gov.in|access-date=2014-10-12|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140119203117/http://www.nia.gov.in/banned_org.aspx|archive-date=2014-01-19}}</ref> ，而[[美國|美國]][[美國國務院|國務院]]則列為「其他受關注團體」<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://2001-2009.state.gov/s/ct/rls/crt/2006/82738.htm|title=Chapter 6 -- Terrorist Organizations|first=Bureau of Public Affairs|last=Department Of State. The Office of Electronic Information|date=2007-04-30|website=2001-2009.state.gov|access-date=2019-12-28}}</ref>。

2009年12月5日，該組織指揮官被印度政府拘捕<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/india/Ulfa-leaders-held-admit-China-link/483340/H1-Article1-483167.aspx |title=Ulfa leaders held, admit China link |work=Hindustan Times |date=2009-12-05 |access-date=2013-01-01 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130217061205/http://www.hindustantimes.com/india/Ulfa-leaders-held-admit-China-link/483340/H1-Article1-483167.aspx |archive-date=2013-02-17 }}</ref>。2011年，於[[孟加拉|孟加拉]]被大規模鎮壓，並開始和印度政府談判<ref>{{cite news |url = http://in.reuters.com/article/idINIndia-53891120110103 |title = ULFA softens demand on Assam independence |work = Reuters |date = 2011-01-03 |access-date = 2011-01-03}}</ref>。2011年9月3日，ULFA、阿薩姆政府和印度政府三方達成停火協議<ref name="Tripartite agreement signed with ULFA">{{cite news|title=Tripartite agreement signed with ULFA|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/article2421033.ece|access-date=2012-09-19|newspaper=The Hindu|date=2011-09-03}}</ref>。

